HEADWORD: Frist
<hw>Frist</hw> <pr>(fr⟦icr⟧st)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>fristen</ets>, <ets>firsten</ets>, to lend, give respite, postpone,
